itemDescription: Welsh rugby union and rugby league footballer

wikipedia_page.main: Jamie Murphy (born 29 December 1989) is a Welsh rugby league player currently for the West Wales Raiders in the RFL League 1.  His position is at centre. He previously played rugby union for Bridgend Ravens & Newport RFC Aberavon Wizards, and Ospreys (3 apps, all in the Anglo-Welsh Cup).
